<body lang=3D"SV" link=3D"#467886" vlink=3D"#96607D" style=3D"word-wrap:bre=
ak-word">
<div class=3D"WordSection1">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Dear friends, <o:p></o:p></span=
></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">(</span><span lang=3D"AR-SA" di=
r=3D"RTL" style=3D"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif">=C7=E1=CA=D1=
=CC=E3=C9 =C7=E1=DA=D1=C8=ED=C9 =C3=CF=E4=C7=E5</span><span dir=3D"LTR"></s=
pan><span dir=3D"LTR"></span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><span dir=3D"LTR"></span>=
<span dir=3D"LTR"></span>)</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p=
>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Greetings from Stockholm! I hop=
e this finds you all well and safe. The world continues to see many challen=
ges, and the last weeks have been particularly difficult in many different =
places, including some were you all
 live. Hope everyone is managing ok, and that you find strength and support=
 from family, friends, and colleagues.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Thanks to all of you who partic=
ipated in the series of network meetings that we held a few weeks back! It =
was lovely to see you all and to hear how everyone was doing. Also great to=
 get everyone=92s thoughts and ideas about
 how you want to use our network structure this coming year. <o:p></o:p></s=
pan></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">I am writing today with three k=
ey updates about the year. You will get information about our digital meeti=
ngs, our in-person meeting, and about our specific activities. There is qui=
te a lot of information in this e-mail
 and I kindly ask you to read through it all, as there are also some <b>que=
stions</b> throughout the e-mail that I would appreciate your answers to.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Before getting into those thing=
s though, I am also happy to share an encouraging update. As you know, we h=
ave been spending a lot of time in the beginning of this year trying to sec=
ure additional funds for our work. This
 morning, we received a letter saying that one of our funding applications =
have been approved! This was the funding we had applied for to do a fourth =
cohort of the learning and exchange program. So in the coming months, we wi=
ll begin recruitment for the next
 group. If you already have people in mind that you think would be good par=
ticipants, please let me know!<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><u><span lang=3D"EN-US">Digital meetings<o:p></o:=
p></span></u></b></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b>=
</p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Based on your feedback in the l=
ast network meeting, we will arrange a digital meeting every other month. T=
his means that this year, we will have one meeting in June, one in August, =
one in October and one in December.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">For each occasion, we will sugg=
est two time slots and you show up to the slot that works best for you. One=
 of the members of the facilitation team, Nabil, we contact you shortly to =
arrange the dates for the first meeting.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">We will use the meetings to sha=
re updates, learn about what is going on in our different contexts, and pro=
vide some training opportunities on specific topics.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">In addition to the regular meet=
ings, some of you expressed an interest to meet digitally in smaller, possi=
bly country specific groups.
<b>For those of you who are interested in this, could you please reply to t=
his e-mail and let me know if you would also be willing to coordinate and h=
ost these meetings?<o:p></o:p></b></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b>=
</p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><u><span lang=3D"EN-US">In-person meeting<o:p></o=
:p></span></u></b></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><u><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p><span style=3D"text-=
decoration:none">&nbsp;</span></o:p></span></u></b></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">We will host our in-person meet=
ing this year in September or October. This will be our one in-person gathe=
ring for this year. Some of you expressed a desire to meet in-person more o=
ften. Unfortunately this is not possible
 due to the funding constraints that we are facing this year, but we will w=
ork to make it possible in the future.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">For the in-person meeting, I wo=
uld like to start checking your availability.
<b>Please write back to me and let me know which of the following dates wou=
ld work for you:
<o:p></o:p></b></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b>=
</p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">September 12-15 <o:p></o:p></sp=
an></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">September 19-22<o:p></o:p></spa=
n></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">September 26-29<o:p></o:p></spa=
n></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">October 3-6<o:p></o:p></span></=
p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">October 10-13<o:p></o:p></span>=
</p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Our group is quite large now an=
d I am sending you multiple suggestions for dates with hope that we can fin=
d one option that work for as many people as possible.
<b>Please let me know all the dates that you are available, and try to be a=
s flexible as possible.
<o:p></o:p></b></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><u><span lang=3D"EN-US">Specific activities<o:p><=
/o:p></span></u></b></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><u><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p><span style=3D"text-=
decoration:none">&nbsp;</span></o:p></span></u></b></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">As you know and as was mentione=
d during our last meeting, we are also planning to run some specific activi=
ties in the different countries this year. There are different timelines to=
 these and different ways of being involved.
 Some of you already have been in meetings about these activities and some =
of you are still waiting to hear how you can be involved.
<b>Given that these activities are country specific, the easiest thing to d=
o if you are interest in knowing more is to contact me directly and I can g=
ive you the information about the activities in your country.</b> As the ye=
ar continues, I will also continue
 to be in touch about these things but if you want to know more already now=
, please don=92t hesitate to contact me. There are also people in our netwo=
rk who are taking specific responsibility for these activities, and I can p=
oint you to them as well for more
 information. <o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Lastly, if you have additional =
ideas (meaning ideas other than those that were discussed at our network me=
eting in Hammamet last year) for specific activities that you would like to=
 implement this year, please let me
 know. As a reminder, below is a short text with the explanation of what th=
ese activities are for:
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin-left:65.2pt"><i><span lang=3D"EN-US"=
>=93In addition to running a capacity-building program (component 1) and ma=
intaining a network comprised of those who completed this program (componen=
t 2), SweFOR=92s work in the Maghreb region
 also includes providing support to strategic interventions that seek to in=
fluence specific key driving factors of conflict (component 3).<o:p></o:p><=
/span></i></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin-left:65.2pt"><i><span lang=3D"EN-US"=
><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></i></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin-left:65.2pt"><i><span lang=3D"EN-US"=
>The strategic interventions are undertaken together with partners in the d=
ifferent contexts and can involve both offering targeted support to some of=
 their ongoing interventions as well as
 designing and implementing new initiatives. These interventions can be led=
 by the partners themselves, by SweFOR, or jointly=94.
<o:p></o:p></span></i></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">So if you have ideas in line wi=
th the criteria above that you and/or your association wants to implement, =
do let me know! The approach to change in our project is based on coming to=
gether for learning, exchange and networking,
 and then on all of you taking that learning and network back to the work t=
hat you are doing in order to make that stronger. From SweFOR=92s side, we =
can provide more targeted support to activities that you suggest if there i=
s an added value to such support.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Thank you for reading through a=
ll of this and looking forward to hearing from you all.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">My very best, <o:p></o:p></span=
></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Erik<o:p></o:p></span></p>
